                <note rend="inline" type="source">710 Consultation 3A/10–744: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Uruguay</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dawson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-10-07">October 7,
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>583. For Sanders. Pan American Union Governing Board at October 5 Meeting
                    accepted the resignation of Argentina from the Political Defense Committee. Peru
                    was designated unanimously to fill the vacancy and is being requested to name a
                    member.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
